And you will not be drinking without saying and asking questions. Thus addressed, then Arjuna, the left-handed Arjuna. Ignoring her words he drank them and fell down
Then Yudhisthira son of Kunti addressed Bhimasena Nakula and Sahadeva are terrible, O scorcher of enemies! They have gone for a long time for the sake of water and do not return, O Arjuna. Bring them too, good luck to you, and you bring the water.
