Neglect of instruction, strength, patience, great weapons in the drone, and humility. If that great soul had fallen under the sway of death I think all others would have been afflicted today
Not here, thinking of anything certain, knowledge, because of the constant combination of action in this world. Who can feel free from doubt about the fall of the preceptor at sunrise
Surely weapons, strength, valor, actions, gold or the ultimate weapons. It is not enough for a man to live happily Similarly his preceptor has been killed by the enemies in battle
He was as bright as the sun of fire and as mighty as Vishnu and Purandara. Brihaspati and Usha were always equal to him but he did not worship that unbearable weapon
O Dhritarashtra, when the young woman cried and cried, when the man was defeated. I know that it is my duty O surgeon therefore depart from the army of the enemies
Where king Arjuna, Satyasandha, Bhimasena, Arjuna, Vasudeva, Satyaki, Srijaya and Yama reside; who can bear them other than me?
