If death, the destroyer of all, should protect him, the son of Pandu, always alert in battle. Either I shall slay him in battle or I shall go with the face of Bhishma to Yama.
If Yama, Varuna, Kubera and Vasava are simultaneously in the great battle. Jugupiṣava comes here to the Pandavas; what to speak of them? I shall conquer him with many of them.
