It is difficult for those who are doing whatever they can to do what is happening O best of the Kurus it is not proper for you to go to the Kurus for no fault
O lord of the earth it is very great for your fault with your son The destruction of the earth is terrible and the kingdom of Yama is increasing
O king you should not grieve over what has arisen from your own fault Even here kings do not protect their lives by any means
The rulers of the earth do not desire the worlds of the virtuous in battle Those who are devoted to heaven enter their armies and fight daily
O great king the destruction of the people began in the morning With one mind listen to him who is like gods and asuras
There were two great archers with great armies and great strength The two eager for battle looked at Iravant
