The sacrifices of the ancestors and the wells and the watering places and the beds. He should always offer gifts to the brahmins in due course
Non-violence, truth, non-anger, obedience to the giver of livelihood. Maintenance of sons and wives purity and non-betrayal Alms should be given for all sacrifices by one who desires prosperity. Great cooking sacrifices should be offered by all thieves
