The unmanifest and the great, and so also the ego. The fifth is earth, air, sky, water and light. Hear from me these eight natures and also their transformations. The fifth is the ear, the skin, the eye, the tongue and the sense of smell. Sound, touch, form, taste and smell. The speech, the hands, the feet, the air, and also the Indra.
